PerlIO-Util/TODO

* PerlIO::reverse - Reads lines reversely

	$in = PerlIO::Util->open('<:reverse', $file);


* PerlIO::dir - Reads directories

	$in = PerlIO::Util->open('<:dir', $dir);


* PerlIO::grep - Reads lines matching a pattern

	$in = PerlIO::Util->open('<:grep(pattern)', $file);

